00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:32,000
 It's actually when you go in front of the people, you go there to be fully present, and it's okay to be fully present and it's okay. And it's actually something that it's supposed to be that your body reflects that you stand up straight, you are in the moment.

9
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:41,000
 You're not shying away from being there with them and transferring any type of knowledge or message that you do have.

